The mixture was transferred into a covered platinum crucible and heated around 850 C for 50 hours. The sample was then air quenched and ground well in an agate mortar. In order to complete the reaction, the same heat treatment was repeated. Warning: Lines with abs(delta 2Theta)>0.06 DEG.
